hex (3 4 11 10 24 25 32 31) ($Nx4 $NyB 2) simpleGrading (1 18 1)
//Block 5: main downstream region bottom
hex (4 5 12 11 25 26 33 32) ($Nx5 $NyB 2) simpleGrading (1 18 1)
//Block 6: outflow region bottom
hex (5 6 13 12 26 27 34 33) ($Nx6 $NyB 2) simpleGrading (1 18 1)

//Block 7: inlet top
hex (7 8 15 14 28 29 36 35) ($Nx1 $NyT 2) simpleGrading (1 1 1)
